{"tid":1757754,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"近排多左好多區議會post，不如建議連仔開個區議會台","createTime":"2019-11-26T16:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T18:26:48.000Z","uid":132217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4d2770396a71e173edc13ce4e91235cad225910e","tid":1757754,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:26:06.000Z","msg":"好似world 台咁，推同意就一齊推啦。<br />\n<br />\n始終lihkg 玩9up創意大過tg group, tg group 一般比較實務太多戰術po<br />\n<br />\n到時集中等區議員收下料，引到區議員辦事處的人mon post <br />\n<br />\n制度內投票係支線，但大家都睇得出支線可以support 返前線先係抗爭大道理！而且到下年立法會選舉由區議員上任到投票只有九個月的時間，分分鐘我地都仲要同佢玩落去，雖要大家的創意同行動力！<br />\n<br />\n同意就一齊推比連仔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果推到成功就可以宣佈第一屆9up 議事堂正式成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac98bd403219d8b31eec2d8cccde2e1af5429281","tid":1757754,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:26:16.000Z","msg":"自推開始"},{"pid":"a06c4b4877bee188c493cc5cd301609997660e20","tid":1757754,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:26:26.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"c8d25afa6b4d635b7eb446e935caf3b69c3ed737","tid":1757754,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:26:37.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"36b1c41b95546a5b03cf8f787e2898360948ec3e","tid":1757754,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:26:48.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"16dcc46cc595ea9a8e0f96ff54cb2311040320c5","tid":1757754,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:27:01.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"1967323b5cdfd89fa4e0957b851c16a9853a288e","tid":1757754,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:27:20.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"94a8e5264e820c5c30054c17bda122de50445942","tid":1757754,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:27:33.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"0bfb5dca4552d53689514682096222e4447d824f","tid":1757754,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:27:47.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"d4869d403f8fb3bf4121c8e4172769525af28756","tid":1757754,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:28:03.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"3749a1fe94166f4057148c8406a8d2cfe1615222","tid":1757754,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:28:21.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"c262abe6cdf833efc45d09956c5a3ea69af69b79","tid":1757754,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:28:34.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"f3493aaec56924904e2367540cdda15c984a055d","tid":1757754,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b7pJdBR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb7pJdBR.jpg&h=6dc1af84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hx9tpJw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHx9tpJw.jpg&h=1bb24b9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好一味屌制度，支線都要贏埋佢<br />\n雙線並行<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />輸左咁多年啦，唔好掉以輕心<br />\nKeep 住和勇不分<br />\n<br />\n勇武主線，制度back up 手足<br />\n<br />\n點解無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6d3270679c95dc21730e48058834784236006d","tid":1757754,"uid":287311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:26:48.000Z","msg":"【請SHARE比你認識既候任區議員必睇呢篇文】<br />\n<br />\n民主派乘著抗爭勢頭橫掃全港議席，馬丁今早跟我說現在贏到開巷的情況，跟1991年與1995年直選也不遑多讓。然而，有多少是政治票，有多少是信任當選人的地區工作，大家可能也心裡有數。<br />\n<br />\n區軒在文章裡寫的提醒，是過去三年南區民主派地區工作者經常會聽到的觀點；而民主派在南區17席贏15席，不計2名暑假起落區的素人及3名現任，10名至少自去年起已開名開樣落區的地區工作者，已有他的支援與指導。<br />\n<br />\n希望他的分享，能幫到每一位候任區議員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/581689778588087/posts/2522642931159419?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F581689778588087%2Fposts%2F2522642931159419%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx91DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=88ce5849\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/581689778588087/posts/2522642931159419?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"}]}